<template>
  <header class="section-header">
    <HeaderLeft :header-data="headerData"></HeaderLeft>
    <HeaderRight
      :count="gameTotal"
      v-show="gameTotal"
      @selectedGroups="selectedGroups"
      @scrollSelector="scrollSelector"
    />
  </header>
</template>
<script lang="ts">
import { defineComponent } from 'vue';
import HeaderLeft from './HeaderLeft.vue';
import HeaderRight from './HeaderRight.vue';
import { getGameGroupResp } from '@/views/home/api/protocol';
export default defineComponent({
  data() {
    return {};
  },
  props: {
    headerData: {
      type: Object as () => getGameGroupResp,
    },
    gameTotal: {
      type: Number,
    },
  },
  methods: {
    selectedGroups() {
      if (this.headerData) {
        this.$router.push(`/casino/originals?groupId=${this.headerData.id}`);
      }
    },
    scrollSelector(text: string) {
      this.$emit('scrollSelector', text, this.headerData!.id);
    },
  },

  components: {
    HeaderLeft,
    HeaderRight,
  },
});
</script>

<style lang="less" scoped>
.section-header {
  display: flex;
  height: 32px;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}
@media only screen and (max-width: 767px) {
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
}
</style>
